&quot;A huge THANK YOU to all the students who signed up and showed up for the 2025 Flames Day of Service! Your time, energy, and kindness made a difference across our community.

From gardening and cleaning at Stone Temple Baptist Church, to planting and beautifying at Maxwell Street Garden, to crafting dog toys and tote bags with the School of Public Health — you’ve proven what it means to be a Flame for others.

Together, we make an impact. Together, we serve. 🙌&nbsp;
&nbsp;
